Title: Weapons | Minewind Wiki | Fandom

Meta Description: Minewind has a very large collection of weapons that can be used to kill other players, or otherwise irritate them. These weapons are classed in categories of Demi-god, God, Legendary, and Mythic. These weapons can be embued with souls, or just generic stats.

Title: Weapons | Minewind Wiki | Fandom

Meta Description: Minewind has a very large collection of weapons that can be used to kill other players, or otherwise irritate them. These weapons are classed in categories of Demi-god, God, Legendary, and Mythic. These weapons can be embued with souls, or just generic stats.
